bonus.description: With enough bonus points acquired, you are able to exchange them for an Upload Credit. The points are then removed from your Bonus Bank and the credit is added to your total uploaded amount.

With enough bonus points acquired, you are able to exchange them for an Upload Credit. The points are then removed from your Bonus Bank and the credit is added to your total uploaded amount.
With enough bonus points acquired, you are able to exchange them for one invite. The points are then removed from your Bonus Bank and the invitation is added to your invite amount.

For 2500.0 Karma Bonus Points you can buy yourself a custom title. the only restrictions are no foul or offensive language or userclass can be entered. The points are then removed from your Bonus Bank and your special title is changed to the title of your choice

Well perhaps you don't need the upload credit, but you know somebody that could use the Karma boost! You are now able to give your Karma credits as a gift! The points are then removed from your Bonus Bank and added to the account of a user of your choice!
And they recieve a PM with all the info as well as who it came from...
With enough bonus points acquired, you can bring the ratio of one torrent to a 1 to 1 ratio! The points are then removed from your Bonus Bank and your status is changed.

We have made many changes to the site, and we hope you enjoy them! We have been working hard to make BitsB somethin' special!

news.headline: Stite Update, design etc

news.body:
I have designed a new unique theme & this present theme is reflecting that. From now on only one theme will be available with BitsB source ( i.e. BitsBv1.0 )
Among other things, I have plans to add sticky news and offers section. Atm I'm working on those 2 things. And XBTT & Ocelet trackers will be integrated in near future. :-)
[color=#990000]Update:[/color] BitsBv1.1 is being coded and will be available publicly in next 4-5 months. :-)
~d6bmg

Best of luck man!

snews.title: Staff News page & security
snews.body:
This page is totally different from the general news page in index, which is available for every user. But this separate news page is available only for staffs (mods+) and url is also part of admin.php Any staff should not give away this url to any user(s) as any user if try to enter this url (page) directly, their account will be auto disabled & warned for infinite period. So, in any case if any user enter this url [b]by mistake[/b] (again I'm saying, they have to [b]prove it[/b]) they [b]may[/b] get their account back in some specific cases, as entering in admin.php or any file(s) that they are not supposed to use will cause the same to every user.
~d6bm4u
